'''[[Maria Wynn]]''' o gwyrghes pan omdhug hi [[Yesu Krist|Yesu]], herwydh dyskasow [[Kristoneth|kristyon]] hag [[islam]]ek. An [[Spyrys Sans]] a's gwrug dhe'n omdhoen, war-lergh Kristonyon; henna o merkyl sempel war-lergh Muslimyon.

